name: Days Ahead
description: Years ago I met a vagrant who spent her entire adult life traveling illegally on CSX trains that she would hop onto and travel from city to city, only hopping off to get food and water or occasionally enjoy the sights of living with that lifestyle. I'm not sure what happened to her but I remember me having a mini-episode about how messed up the world truly was and I'll never forget when she looked directly at me and with a very hazy gaze said that no matter how messy the days are ahead that the sun will always rise again no matter what happens.
